summary: I decided to change Ysolda, because she needed a makeover :3
descriptionHtml:
I did the same thing that i did with uthgerd, there\'s not really that much that i can say about it.

Ysolda didn\'t look... too bad... before, but i thought that i could change her up a little bit so she would look better.

REQUIRES APACHII SKY HAIR: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168
